</P>
<P>
VENTURA -- Lake Casitas, Reyes Creek, Rose Valley Lakes, Upper Sespe Creek. 
</P>
<P>
SAN LUIS OBISPO -- Atascadero Lake, Laguna Lake, Lake Lopez. 
</P>
<P>
INYO -- Cottonwood Creek, Diaz Lake, Georges Creek, Independence Creek, Lone 
Pine Creek, Tuttle Creek. 
</P>
