<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Carolco Pictures Inc.: The Los Angeles entertainment company's 1988 profit more 
than doubled to $36 million from $14 million the previous year. Revenue rose 
59% to $165 million. The results were boosted by feature films revenue, which 
more than doubled to $139 million, increased equity from its LIVE Entertainment 
Inc. affiliate, higher demand for American films abroad and the modernization 
of overseas theaters. 
</P>
</TEXT>
