<TEXT>
<P>
Barclays Bank of New York announced that James P. Gay, Stanley J. Nawrocki and 
Nicholas J. DeMeo have been promoted from senior vice president to executive 
vice president. The announcement was made by John S. Spencer, chief executive 
of Barclays USA banking division and president of BBNY, the bank's New York 
commercial and retail banking subsidiary. 
