Table, 1988-89 REGULAR SEASON RECAP; Table, 1988-89 RESULTS; Photo, COLOR, John 
Tonelli, who played on four NHL championship teams with the New York Islanders, 
is one of several players the Kings have acquired to increase their playoff 
experience. MIKE MEADOWS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Mike Krushelnyski, being 
checked by Toronto's Todd Gill, will give the Kings added experience in NHL 
playoffs starting today. JAYNE KAMIN-ONCEA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
